    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Describes the culture of a Pre-Columbian people associated with an archaeological site in western Bolivia. It was the capital of an empire that flourished from CE 300 to CE 1000.</Note_Text>
